{"tid":1185280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6月9出嚟有撚用咩？嘥氣","createTime":"2019-06-04T07:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T09:59:25.000Z","uid":191290,"like":90,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fb55a14e1a91ff82e6acf9401c5bd89c358afc25","tid":1185280,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:32:54.000Z","msg":"我哋進入咗決定香港生死存亡嘅一個個星期啦，無論你係咩立場，有番說話我好想同大家講，文長亦有啲1999，但句句都係肺腑之言。<br />\n<br />\n香港有好多人都鍾意睇Avengers，覺得裡面嘅角色好熱血，甚至對Ironman嘅犧牲耿耿於懷。<br />\n<br />\n喺無限之戰之後，大部分嘅英雄都消失咗，淨返落嚟嘅，有人面對唔到失敗，自暴自棄。有人過上新生活，有家庭，有妻兒，唔想再令自己同身邊嘅人身陷險境。有人無參與戰鬥，唔知發生咩事，只知道身邊嘅人莫名消失咗。亦都有人..一直唔放棄，花盡力氣希望扭轉命運，望返我哋香港人，其實有啲相似。<br />\n<br />\n睇戲，當見到有啲角色想逃避，心裡面會好希望佢醒。因為你知道即使佢哋有能力，但唔團結，一樣會輸，你好想睇到佢哋贏，觀眾都希望超級英雄會係勝利嘅一方。<br />\n<br />\n逃犯條例嘅事件發生以嚟，令人最心痛嘅言論唔係來自支持修例嘅一方，而係你明明反對，明明知道要抗爭，但講出口嘅卻係呢啲說話：<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">「之前咪試過囉！都唔得！」「搞嚟做咩吖，都過硬咖啦！」「又係呢啲，我瞓下好過！」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果Avengers都係咁諗，大家仲邊會睇到第四集呢？有人可能會話：「屌，戲嚟咖嘛，鍾意寫到點樣扭轉乾坤都得咖啦！」但你有無諗過，佢哋贏嘅係每個人心裡面都有一份信念一直堅持住。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭從來唔會一次就成功，唔好覺得自己係為咗其他人先出嚟，為嘅係我哋都相信嘅事，仲有我哋共同擁有嘅身分 &mdash; <span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\nAvengers嘅Endgame好齊人，香港嘅Endgame都唔可以無咗「你」，一齊重新拎起你嘅雷神搥啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mCChBL8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmCChBL8.gif&h=5e274abc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ZdTUxP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ZdTUxP.gif&h=e752c208&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<br />\n-簽完記得確認返電郵<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=667145bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n學界反送中聯署集合<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/%E5%AD%B8%E7%95%8C%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%2590%2588%25E9%259B%2586&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=693a3f03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/%E5%AD%B8%E7%95%8C%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86</a><br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道"},{"pid":"551479d2de7ca37b1aa7e3c3a1a4f687d43719d5","tid":1185280,"uid":244332,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=88b0fdfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6/9，香港人，銅鑼灣見"},{"pid":"257e65f0a4a4422ee6027c018e0751fd86195084","tid":1185280,"uid":191290,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"551479d2de7ca37b1aa7e3c3a1a4f687d43719d5","tid":1185280,"uid":244332,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=88b0fdfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6/9，香港人，銅鑼灣見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"住得係呢片土地，係有職責咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5dc1551234e0392b18ae54786b4701168ae98c","tid":1185280,"uid":122134,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:35:59.000Z","msg":"on your left"},{"pid":"286b7103eb6217e71ea02c592a7f1bf903a2cacc","tid":1185280,"uid":18245,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kop7Y2W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkop7Y2W.jpg&h=80e66f15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"250d361ee8f13ecb9c909d71403a1e3c492d9a78","tid":1185280,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:43:52.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望多啲人睇到"},{"pid":"f01e0be4b920a9c30213edfb9b836a9321208e12","tid":1185280,"uid":52705,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:01:39.000Z","msg":"三十年前既雞蛋對上高墻，到今時今日依然企係雞蛋一方呢個立場我理解，但點解年初一既時候又光速割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實借avengers套戲黎宣傳唔覺得好嘔心核突咩?<br />\n根本香港同avengers兩者黎類比就係不恰當，我真係未見過avengers會向弱者抽刀"},{"pid":"d264c6348eb4a1331f9b0962f87f928179d01532","tid":1185280,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:03:23.000Z","msg":"集合地點唔係改左維園？"},{"pid":"fb98e6dc9f0220ce65500601d0519acbdb718caf","tid":1185280,"uid":238551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:09:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d22eef4151c376fc9aef162bac026e96f61c0e4","tid":1185280,"uid":48143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2754e4d6522bc417147ab21b451957241ee24cd","tid":1185280,"uid":13013,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:12:32.000Z","msg":"發神經 講咁多懶係振奮人心既野<br />\n出到黎就行完番屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f836e92f9f5583b5b7a78c0876f8c44172ffb385","tid":1185280,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:14:04.000Z","msg":"警犬迫民陣將起點改咗喺維園呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57c5ac570209d6f00f6f26e660a77e361baa8a4","tid":1185280,"uid":191290,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f01e0be4b920a9c30213edfb9b836a9321208e12","tid":1185280,"uid":52705,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:01:39.000Z","msg":"三十年前既雞蛋對上高墻，到今時今日依然企係雞蛋一方呢個立場我理解，但點解年初一既時候又光速割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實借avengers套戲黎宣傳唔覺得好嘔心核突咩?<br />\n根本香港同avengers兩者黎類比就係不恰當，我真係未見過avengers會向弱者抽刀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"其實我只係用緊一個香港小市民嘅角度，去講自己嘅心聲。對於我嚟講，係接近滅亡之前、再糾纏喺過往嘅分裂、鬥爭意義並唔大，最重要大家都係真心想保住香港就已經應該走出嚟。我信嘅唔係任何一個政黨權威，係自己覺得啱嘅事，盡一個市民嘅責任。<br />\n<br />\n我哋當然同avengers唔一樣，至少我哋無異於常人嘅能力，但真係無引發到反思同值得學習嘅地方嗎？"},{"pid":"7c218ba34c0238d3abaa0206accc875dd166b157","tid":1185280,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d264c6348eb4a1331f9b0962f87f928179d01532","tid":1185280,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:03:23.000Z","msg":"集合地點唔係改左維園？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:18:23.000Z","msg":"手快快copy錯咗舊個段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c553598f04fc08a03928794e1b0254f2575037","tid":1185280,"uid":13395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c218ba34c0238d3abaa0206accc875dd166b157","tid":1185280,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d264c6348eb4a1331f9b0962f87f928179d01532","tid":1185280,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:03:23.000Z","msg":"集合地點唔係改左維園？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:18:23.000Z","msg":"手快快copy錯咗舊個段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:20:55.000Z","msg":"民陣公布遊行安排如下：<br />\n<br />\n遊行起點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）<br />\n<br />\n遊行路線：維園草地起點＞高士威道＞禮頓街＞伊榮街＞邊寧頓街＞軒尼詩道西行車路＞金鐘道＞樂禮街＞夏愨道＞添美道＞立法會外行人路終點<br />\n<br />\n集合時間：下午2時半<br />\n<br />\n起步時間：下午3時（或維園草地達八成滿）"},{"pid":"6230525e108a05f67f54465d10cc788b61362910","tid":1185280,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb98e6dc9f0220ce65500601d0519acbdb718caf","tid":1185280,"uid":238551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:09:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:26:27.000Z","msg":"你care嗎？"},{"pid":"6bda5b8e3798ffe8e53f5b90ef6acd57b11d0b31","tid":1185280,"uid":238551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:52:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"504e2710d371e75b7d29e47d097b55bec5427146","tid":1185280,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6bda5b8e3798ffe8e53f5b90ef6acd57b11d0b31","tid":1185280,"uid":238551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6230525e108a05f67f54465d10cc788b61362910","tid":1185280,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb98e6dc9f0220ce65500601d0519acbdb718caf","tid":1185280,"uid":238551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:09:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:26:27.000Z","msg":"你care嗎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:52:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:18:34.000Z","msg":"咁就夠啦，多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40323b30ed3f44b858c3ada09ff975e9f155714","tid":1185280,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b57c5ac570209d6f00f6f26e660a77e361baa8a4","tid":1185280,"uid":191290,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f01e0be4b920a9c30213edfb9b836a9321208e12","tid":1185280,"uid":52705,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:01:39.000Z","msg":"三十年前既雞蛋對上高墻，到今時今日依然企係雞蛋一方呢個立場我理解，但點解年初一既時候又光速割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實借avengers套戲黎宣傳唔覺得好嘔心核突咩?<br />\n根本香港同avengers兩者黎類比就係不恰當，我真係未見過avengers會向弱者抽刀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"其實我只係用緊一個香港小市民嘅角度，去講自己嘅心聲。對於我嚟講，係接近滅亡之前、再糾纏喺過往嘅分裂、鬥爭意義並唔大，最重要大家都係真心想保住香港就已經應該走出嚟。我信嘅唔係任何一個政黨權威，係自己覺得啱嘅事，盡一個市民嘅責任。<br />\n<br />\n我哋當然同avengers唔一樣，至少我哋無異於常人嘅能力，但真係無引發到反思同值得學習嘅地方嗎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:24:30.000Z","msg":"我唔知其他人點諗，但我至少行過幾次七一係得出咁既諗法<br />\n咁多年黎民陣攪既遊行都係比人騎劫緊，我唔明白點解一個遊行係可以咁嘉年華化，5步一枝政黨既旗，我都仲接受到，10步一個政黨既錢箱，仲有D政黨元老既焦點竟然係放左係叫人入錢而唔係個遊行目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好自然就會有種無力感，佢根本唔係想成功，個遊行成效亦都唔大，亦都有種好似比人利用既感覺，而個感覺係十分之差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49553fd6f6df9ad9fe77c102f013b5f72d715097","tid":1185280,"uid":140709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:55:13.000Z","msg":"我幫你推～<br />\n<br />\nBy 俾你幫過嘅人"},{"pid":"ca11768173adf10863c66cad8ba75cb0b1321fa9","tid":1185280,"uid":191290,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d40323b30ed3f44b858c3ada09ff975e9f155714","tid":1185280,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b57c5ac570209d6f00f6f26e660a77e361baa8a4","tid":1185280,"uid":191290,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f01e0be4b920a9c30213edfb9b836a9321208e12","tid":1185280,"uid":52705,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:01:39.000Z","msg":"三十年前既雞蛋對上高墻，到今時今日依然企係雞蛋一方呢個立場我理解，但點解年初一既時候又光速割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實借avengers套戲黎宣傳唔覺得好嘔心核突咩?<br />\n根本香港同avengers兩者黎類比就係不恰當，我真係未見過avengers會向弱者抽刀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"其實我只係用緊一個香港小市民嘅角度，去講自己嘅心聲。對於我嚟講，係接近滅亡之前、再糾纏喺過往嘅分裂、鬥爭意義並唔大，最重要大家都係真心想保住香港就已經應該走出嚟。我信嘅唔係任何一個政黨權威，係自己覺得啱嘅事，盡一個市民嘅責任。<br />\n<br />\n我哋當然同avengers唔一樣，至少我哋無異於常人嘅能力，但真係無引發到反思同值得學習嘅地方嗎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:24:30.000Z","msg":"我唔知其他人點諗，但我至少行過幾次七一係得出咁既諗法<br />\n咁多年黎民陣攪既遊行都係比人騎劫緊，我唔明白點解一個遊行係可以咁嘉年華化，5步一枝政黨既旗，我都仲接受到，10步一個政黨既錢箱，仲有D政黨元老既焦點竟然係放左係叫人入錢而唔係個遊行目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好自然就會有種無力感，佢根本唔係想成功，個遊行成效亦都唔大，亦都有種好似比人利用既感覺，而個感覺係十分之差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:55:50.000Z","msg":"的確係有呢啲情況，好多錢箱、好多旗。覺得唔值得支持嘅，你可以選擇比隻中指佢哋。但你睇返每次遊行，係咪真係無用？23條、反國教等等，其實我哋係有成功過，而全世界都知道。你出嚟遊行嘅目的係咩？感覺被騎劫固然係難受，但因為咁樣而選擇噤聲，違背自己嘅初衷，向極權低頭，承受種種荒謬嘅制度時，你會唔會更難受？<br />\n<br />\n國際間都留意緊呢件事，雖然我唔會覺得咁多個國家出聲係因為想幫香港，每個人都會為自己利益去做一啲嘢，但趁著世界都肯支出力持我哋嘅時候，作為當時人，我哋暫時放低成見好嗎？"},{"pid":"39914765ffe6322a840bc6cc87abd470d32cf2c5","tid":1185280,"uid":221171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nVFV8Hm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVFV8Hm.jpg&h=a1425513&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a53bd29855524ac6eaa29c4022d896bfd621cf37","tid":1185280,"uid":191290,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49553fd6f6df9ad9fe77c102f013b5f72d715097","tid":1185280,"uid":140709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:55:13.000Z","msg":"我幫你推～<br />\n<br />\nBy 俾你幫過嘅人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:59:25.000Z","msg":"到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}